title: Drawing, "Flatware Handles"
description:
Sixteen designs for table flatware handles, encompassing both unadorned and
ornate styles, occupy the entire page. Designs are place horzontally in the left half and vertically in the right.

tombstone.epitaph:
Drawing, "Flatware Handles".
35.2 x 42.5 cm (13 7/8 x 16 3/4 in.). Gift of Ellen Gustav Jensen. 1956-47-35.
